ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model

Class Servodrive

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model.APhysicalComponent
      • ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model.Servodrive

  • public class Servodrive
extends APhysicalComponent
    General Spindle model class. Implements the physical model of a Servodrive. Inputlist: 1: State : [-] : On/Off 2: RotSpeed : [rpm] : Actual rotational speed 3: Torque : [Nm] : Actual torque Outputlist: 1: PTotal : [W] : Calculated total energy demand 2: PLoss : [W] : Calculated power loss 3: PUse : [W] : Calculated mechanical power 4: TemperatureOut : [K] : Coolant outlet temperature Config parameters: TODO
    Author:
    sizuest
